OL,3,CNew US owners for Exeter Chiefs as
OL,4,Ctakeover goes through
OL,6,FThe chief executive of the Exeter
OL,7,FChiefs has insisted the club's
OL,8,Ffinancial position has been
OL,9,Fstrengthened following its sale to
OL,10,FBlack Knight Rugby, whose US-based
OL,11,Fparent company are owners of Premier
OL,12,FLeague side Bournemouth.
OL,14,FTony Rowe, who has financially
OL,15,Fsupported the club for 25 years, said
OL,16,FUS investment will allow the club to
OL,17,Fpay off debts, improve facilities at
OL,18,FSandy Park and invest in the squad.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
