OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1782915513
OL,3,CNew US owners for Exeter Chiefs as
OL,4,Ctakeover goes through
OL,6,FThe announcement comes ten days after
OL,7,Fthe Devon club lost 26-17 to
OL,8,FNorthampton in the Prem Rugby final.
OL,10,FUnder Black Knight, Tony Rowe will
OL,11,Fcontinue as chief executive, which
OL,12,FExeter said would help "maintain
OL,13,Fcontinuity", as part of a three-person
OL,14,Fexecutive board alongside Cannae
OL,15,FHoldings vice chairman William Foley
OL,16,Fand CEO Ryan Caswell.
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@KO]
