CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1782915513
OL,3,CNew US owners for Exeter Chiefs as
OL,4,Ctakeover goes through
OL,6,F"If you had to choose an investor in
OL,7,Fthe world of sport, you could not
OL,8,Fchoose better than Black Knight. I am
OL,9,Fabsolutely over the moon," said former
OL,10,Ftelecoms business owner Rowe.
OL,12,F"With Black Knight, we can look
OL,13,Fforward to a positive future, building
OL,14,Fon what we have already achieved to
OL,15,Fkeep pushing for success on and off
OL,16,Fthe pitch."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@ZO]tD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
