OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1782915513
OL,3,CNew US owners for Exeter Chiefs as
OL,4,Ctakeover goes through
OL,6,FHe added: "We have been under funded
OL,7,Ffor the last four or five years and to
OL,8,Fhave an investor come in, like Black
OL,9,FNight Rugby, who are probably one of
OL,10,Fthe best sports investors around at
OL,11,Fthe moment - is massively significant
OL,12,Ffor us. We need to move on now and
OL,13,FBlack Knight Rugby will be able to
OL,14,Ffund that for us. It is going to be an
OL,15,Fexciting season coming up."
OL,17,FMr Rowe said he was optimistic about
OL,18,Fthe future of Prem rugby - forecasting
OL,19,Fa situation where the league could
OL,20,Fexpand to 12, 14 or even 16 teams.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
